{"tid":166861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海關元朗搗大麻包裝分銷中心　夫婦涉販毒被捕","createTime":"2017-03-22T12:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T18:09:00.000Z","uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfcc67af3315f68f9d3c0c76195e853bf5077c87","tid":166861,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:21:41.000Z","msg":"關搗破元朗一間大麻包裝及分銷中心，檢獲4.5公斤懷疑大麻花，市值約86萬元。<br />\n海關毒品調查科探員今早在元朗區進行反毒品行動，截查一名目標男子，並在其所攜帶的黑色膠袋內，檢獲少量大麻花。他其後被押回寓所搜查，海關在單位內發現一名女子，並搜獲大量大麻花及一批包裝工具。行動中，海關共檢獲4.5公斤懷疑大麻花，市值約86萬元。<br />\n被捕的兩人為夫婦，分別47及41歲，男子報稱任職裝修工人，女子則報稱為護士，他們涉嫌販毒被帶返署扣查。海關正追查毒品來源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://toronto.singtao.ca/1620867/2017-03-22/post-%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%90%97%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D%E5%88%86%E9%8A%B7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%80%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E6%B6%89%E8%B2%A9%E6%AF%92%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftoronto.singtao.ca%2F1620867%2F2017-03-22%2Fpost-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2590%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%258C%2585%25E8%25A3%259D%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%258A%25B7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B2%25A9%25E6%25AF%2592%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2e306868\" target=\"_blank\">http://toronto.singtao.ca/1620867/2017-03-22/post-%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%90%97%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D%E5%88%86%E9%8A%B7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%80%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E6%B6%89%E8%B2%A9%E6%AF%92%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"389309aca2b84293aa9c0f59a6ac62a82e420c57","tid":166861,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"連登班道友仲唔出黎保釋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3620db29939aeacb0329396c375691a215f316","tid":166861,"uid":24457,"like":0,"